	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Oct 12th 4:50 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.95]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Best exp at those levels are by far the dungeon zones. SolA, SolB, Mistmoore, Dalnir, Droga, Nurga, and Echo are all good.<br><br>Expect to solo a lot though because at least on my server many of these zones are empty much of the time.<br><br><br>You'll generally want to be careful at first until you've learned the area you fight in, and even then expect to die a few times before learning the area. I'd probably go with standard normal play, chain pets if you're conj specced, or plan burning if you're not. chaining is generally more effeicient though if you can pull singles reliably (not always the case in most dungeons) If you chain, if you don't have an enshrouded veil get one ASAP, they're not to expensive and make a world of difference.<br><br>In dungeons where mobs run it's important to time a nuke near the end of the fight to keep a mob from running, or use an earth pet. Pre 50 earth kinda sucks though unless yer chaining.<br><br>Hope that helps a a bit.<br><br><br>Kranken, Archmage<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
